  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_human_tissue_authority">Human Tissue Authority</xref>
 is an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_human_tissue_authority">Human Tissue Authority</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_human_tissue_authority">HTA</xref>) is an executive agency of the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_department_of_health_and_social_care">Department of Health and Social Care</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_human_tissue_authority">Human Tissue Authority</xref>
 is the regulator for human 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_tissue">TISSUE</xref>
 and organs.        </p>
      <p>
For further information on the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_human_tissue_authority">Human Tissue Authority</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_human_tissue_authority">Human Tissue Authority</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.hta.gov.uk/about-us"
               scope="external"
               format="html">About Us.</xref>
      </p>
  </div>
